title: Fourth Annual Marc Sessler Mock Draft
itunes:title: Fourth Annual Marc Sessler Mock Draft
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal bring you the most anticipated piece of draft content each year: Sessler's annual mock draft. Later, Spice Rack joins to share his thoughts and predictions about this year's draft class.
